From 770e40ff44be5a0c66dde2f90573448f7acc14a2 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Thu, 7 May 2026 20:45:45 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: add admin dashboard for request management

- Add Supabase integration for persistent data storage
- Create authentication system with SHA256 password hashing
- Build admin dashboard with request listing, filtering, and pagination
- Add request detail view with status management and notes
- Create metrics endpoint showing request statistics
- Integrate database save into PDF analysis flow
- Add password hash generation script
- Add comprehensive setup documentation
- Support UTM-based fine amount calculations

All features are production-ready and deployed to admin route.
